AdditionalResource.Name: Settings
AdditionalResource.Description: Global settings for the entire TicTacToe project

AdditionalResource.Name: AdditionalResources
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of additional resources used by the project

AdditionalResource.Name: Entities
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of entities in the project (Player, Opponent, Game, Mark, Win, Loss, etc)

AdditionalResource.Name: LanguageTokens
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of language tokens used in the app.

AdditionalResource.Name: AILevels
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of AI Levels which the game supports starting with None (no ai) and working up to an AI that will win or tie every game.

AdditionalResource.Name: AIStrategies
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of strategies used by the AI, and which AI levels that start be used at.

AdditionalResource.Name: Translations
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of transaltions which any implementation of this game needs to support

AdditionalResource.Name: Cells
AdditionalResource.Description: A formal list of the cells in the 3x3 game of tic tac toe.

AdditionalResource.Name: CellPatterns
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of cells and a target if a match is found.

AdditionalResource.Name: CellStates
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of states that a cell can have

AdditionalResource.Name: TranslationTests
AdditionalResource.Description: These values validate the rotate and flip index values

AdditionalResource.Name: TargetPlatforms
AdditionalResource.Description: A list of target platforms that the SDK will support
